PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Antjuan Pierre JACKSON, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 156502
COA: 332307 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 5, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellant to extend the time for filing his supplement brief is GRANTED. The supplemental brief will be accepted as timely filed if submitted on or before January 30, 2019.
